      <title>美国参议员寻求加强向中国出售储备石油的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senators-seek-harden-ban-selling-reserve-oil-china-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员周四提出立法，加强禁止从战略石油储备（SPR）向中国出售原油的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senators-seek-harden-ban-selling-reserve-oil-china-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
